author: Discovery
description:
Josh dives the deadly, frigid waters of the Baltic Sea in search of a revolutionary Nazi submarine: the V-80. Hitler ordered it scuttled to prevent the Allies from learning its secrets. Now, Josh risks it all to bring the prototype to the surface. #ExpeditionUnknown Wednesdays at 9P.
